{"tid":534221,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[一齊倒恒管米]垃圾恒管討論區","createTime":"2018-01-19T14:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T13:12:32.000Z","uid":31521,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dee461dccfaf0bd1e7b2a867febec02d086f91ab","tid":534221,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"唔好睇佢好新淨咁 其實恒管都幾垃圾下<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">校舍篇</span><br />\n依山而建 分A B M N D 5幢building<br />\n幾幢之間冇天橋連住 亦都冇瓦遮頭<br />\n而且要行斜路 仲要同車share路<br />\n返學轉堂落堂落雨冇帶遮更加gg<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/223247_fa2eef55e1e8501429dc70283aed35a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F223247_fa2eef55e1e8501429dc70283aed35a5.png&h=24698305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">宿舍篇</span><br />\n新淨 有獨立廁所<br />\n但房設計好有問題 例如消防喉位置<br />\n廁所去水出水慢 渠又成日塞<br />\nd房成日一陣味 宿費貴但環境差<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/224538_71e87e8d7f5c439cf17d283e4e93d9b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F224538_71e87e8d7f5c439cf17d283e4e93d9b7.png&h=36451283&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/224540_be1f94b4c630a8497428ce376ec6b7ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F224540_be1f94b4c630a8497428ce376ec6b7ee.png&h=5237345d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/224541_ae76d74102a07ac0073f309eacc2668c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F224541_ae76d74102a07ac0073f309eacc2668c.png&h=6ed6457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n垃圾學店缺點多 又多唔讀書嘅死mk 仲有班成日打丁話恒管好快正名嘅高層 歡迎其他ching一齊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d14622a76bada5a0b6a9c8aeb2db4e9c1f946d","tid":534221,"uid":31521,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:56:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">管理篇</span><br />\n有個支持國歌法嘅奶共校長<br />\n帶領一大班教職員為恒管升格打丁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/225254_0ebe2958b215b6189edcc25a60a9ba77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F225254_0ebe2958b215b6189edcc25a60a9ba77.png&h=b4352ffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRegistry SAO班冗員十問九唔識答<br />\n日日準時返工放工 收5點 你4:58入去佢都趕你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個sem都係有排都未到deadline就催你交學費<br />\n想申請遲交學費都又呢又路"},{"pid":"2d5d996da4f25a5913b351583f563d44dce2eae2","tid":534221,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T17:57:27.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94fd1708afcb37203f537788f92062a962dfbff","tid":534221,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"4人hall?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c9cdd8e9f2223e0aba19f8ed779c7b0756cfd0","tid":534221,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f94fd1708afcb37203f537788f92062a962dfbff","tid":534221,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"4人hall?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T01:42:08.000Z","msg":"2 3 4人都有"},{"pid":"ec4c54eff90b5cafa0db67eee7e541ce53250d23","tid":534221,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"呢間野其實幾耐？年年講升格<br />\n另一間垃圾係珠海"},{"pid":"c5e6107e29a7b58d3cd920299a3acb940d99fd6a","tid":534221,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"